  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>A shaman who selects the tribe spirit strives to protect her allies, whether they be a traditional tribal unit or a chosen group of adventuring companions.</em><br><br><strong>Spirit Magic Spells:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.wa0zb2pncesmm9lz]{Bless} (1st),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.menqakfoa1ftvi3f]{Shield Other} (2nd),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.qn947hen3wrelxhz]{Create Food and Water} (3rd),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.0lrux8tmaml5fkw6]{Spiritual Ally} (4th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.f6lqt3ju8m7r5la2]{Life Bubble} (5th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.eg3i21asvo69mbma]{Battlemind Link} (6th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.aqeaxoaozlv9vg35]{Vision} (7th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.gw2sgj93dgarpem8]{Discern Location} (8th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.klcvk9ct1l7mhjwp]{Heal, Mass} (9th).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Spirit Animal: </strong>The shaman’s spirit animal has colorations or markings that resemble a totem or important symbol for the shaman’s tribe. When the spirit animal successfully performs the aid another action, the bonus it provides increases by 1.</p>",
